Sentencas: In this study, 10 mol% Cu2+-doped SnP2O7 was compounded with K2CO3 to prepare Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 composite electrolyte.
Titulo: Characterization and electrical properties of a novel Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 composite electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The structure, morphology and medium temperature electrical properties of Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 were investigated.
Titulo: Characterization and electrical properties of a novel Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 composite electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Raman spectrometer result showed that Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 was composed of pyrophosphate and metaphosphate groups.
Titulo: Characterization and electrical properties of a novel Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 composite electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum conductivity of Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 reached 6.6 x10(-2) S.cm(-1) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Characterization and electrical properties of a novel Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 composite electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density of Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 reached to 131 mW.cm(-2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Characterization and electrical properties of a novel Sn0.9Cu0.1P2O7/KPO3 composite electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
